                     <interp inst="t18220109-28-person304" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A porter gave them to me in Newgate-market, to carry to a butcher's - Debenham swears false.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18220109-28-verdict148" type="verdictDescription">
